---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<style>
  .hero-section__container {
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .solution-section__container {
    gap: 40px;
  }
</style>

<PageLayout
  title="Sushi Restaurant Web Design Experts | About Us | HappyRoll"
  description="Learn more about HappyRoll and our mission to help sushi restaurants succeed online with top-notch web design and marketing."
>
  <main class="bg-neutral-100">
    <section id="hero-section" class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-section__container pv4 ph3 center flex-l mw8 pt5-l">
        <h1
          class="neutral-800 f3 f2-ns lh-title mt0-l fw6 mw6 w-50-l mw-none-l center tc tl-l"
        >
          Transform Your Sushi Restaurant's Success with HappyRoll
        </h1>

        <p
          class="neutral-600 lh-copy sans-serif center measure-wide mw-none-l tc w-50-l tl-l mt0-l"
        >
          Running a sushi restaurant is challenging—standing out in a crowded
          market, attracting diners, and ensuring your online presence truly
          reflects the quality of your food. You need more than just a website;
          you need a partner who understands the unique demands of your business
          and can help you succeed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="solution-section" class="solution-section">
      <div
        class="solution-section__container pt4 pb5 ph3 flex flex-column flex-row-l mw8 center pb6-l"
      >
        <div class="mw6 center">
          <img
            src="/images/sushi-chefs-working.webp"
            alt="Sushi chefs rolling sushi."
            width="268"
            height="178.7"
            class="br4 w-100 h-100"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="solution-section__left-column mw6 center">
          <h2 class="f4 f3-ns f2-l neutral-800 lh-title fw6">
            {"Why HappyRoll?".toTitleCase()}
          </h2>

          <p class="neutral-600 lh-copy sans-serif">
            At HappyRoll, we specialize in providing sushi restaurants with
            top-tier digital marketing solutions that drive real results. Our
            team of experienced developers and marketers knows the ins and outs
            of the restaurant industry.
          </p>
          <p class="neutral-600 lh-copy sans-serif">
            We've crafted a complete, tailored service that includes custom
            website design, social media management, Google Business Profile
            optimization, and much more—all designed to bring more diners to
            your door.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
